title: ICE after a type named `Request` has already been imported in this module

labels.name: I-ICE
labels.description: Issue: The compiler panicked, giving an Internal Compilation Error (ICE) ❄️

body:
I tried this code:
https://github.com/posix4e/curl-rust/tree/bug_report

I expected the code not to compile but I didn't expect the Internal compiler error

src/http/mod.rs:2 pub use self::multi_handle::{MultiHandle,Request};
                                                           ^~~~~~~
